{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"header":"Can it be temporary?","text_size":"h5","content":"<p>Yes. Freestanding tri- and quad-fold dividers can be set in place when needed and stored away just as easily. They’re ideal for renters or anyone who wants flexibility without installation.<\/p>","content_page":"","open":false}},"item_c7PiG6":{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"header":"Is it worth the price?","text_size":"h5","content":"<p>Yes. Unlike plastic or metal gates that bend, break, or get tucked out of sight, these are permanent pieces of furniture — built to belong in your home. Made from solid hardwood with time-honored joinery, they last for years and age gracefully alongside the rest of your woodwork.<\/p>","content_page":"","open":false}}},"block_order":["item_kBd4Rx","item_3WgcNk","item_XLg4mk","item_Kgf9Ka","item_rzKrD4","item_c7PiG6"],"name":"Collapsible tabs","settings":{"container":"container","color_scheme":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_17_1.png","image_position":"left","column_gap":100,"heading":"Common Questions,  Straight Answers","heading_size":"h5","subheading":"","description":"","header_alignment":"left","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"animations":"inherit","custom_class":"pt-80 py-120  common-questions-section"}},"help_cta_split_trYaHm":{"type":"help-cta-split","name":"Questions \/ Help CTA","settings":{"heading":"Questions about millwork?","text":"We’ve helped homeowners match historic trim, size details to the right scale, and choose profiles that feel original to the home.\n<br>\n<br>\nIf you’d like a second set of eyes before ordering, we’re happy to walk through it with you.","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_55.png","section_class":"py-80 questions-about-section","primary_label":"Order now","primary_link":"#MainContent","secondary_label":"Talk to a Craftsman","secondary_link":"https:\/\/cms.vintagedoors.com\/support"}}},"order":["breadcrumb_LYVrF9","main","features","measurement_guide_WHBMF8"